    {
      "question": "writing sample one: submit an op-ed (or similar piece of writing), 800 words or fewer, that demonstrates your ability to structure an argument and cites relevant data and research to substantiate your position.. please copy the text of the piece—not just a hyperlink to an external source—into the box below. note: if you don’t have an op-ed or personal essay in your portfolio, we suggest you write one about an issue you care about. here are two examples of op-eds we like: • farzon nahvi, \"i'm a doctor and even i can't afford my student loans\" https://www.nytimes.com/2018/08/20/opinion/medical-school-student-loans-tuition-debt-doctor.html • ted gup, \"the world has already seen 'fire and fury'\" https://www.washingtonpost.com/opinions/the-world-has-already-seen-fire-and-fury/2017/08/11/b4d7f98c-7e17-11e7-83c7-5bd5460f0d7e_story.html?utm_term=.e69f4f0307c1",
